\frac{2}{\pi}\int_{-1}^{+1}\frac{\T_{n}(x)\T_{m}(x)}{\sqrt{1-x^{2}}}\tic x=\frac{2}{\pi}\int_{\varphi=0}^{\pi}\cos(n\varphi)\cos(m\varphi)\tic\varphi\]

